Your duty, sir, is to fire when you're told to fire.

167
00:06:01,990 --> 00:06:03,810
您的职责  就是在祖国需要的时候
Your duty, sir, is to be the strong

168
00:06:03,810 --> 00:06:05,760
毫不迟疑地强力出击
and unwavering fist of our nation.

169
00:06:05,760 --> 00:06:08,060
为什么他们通过南极紧急通讯网下达命令
Why'd they send the orders through the Antarctic channel?

170
00:06:09,360 --> 00:06:10,560
为什么他们朝我们开火
Why would they fire on us?

171
