我只是个水手
I'm a sailor.

172
00:06:12,410 --> 00:06:13,630
我没资格质疑这些
I don't have the luxury to ask.

173
00:06:13,630 --> 00:06:14,640
是的  你没有
No, you don't,

174
00:06:14,810 --> 00:06:16,850
所以你只是个水手长  而我才是艇长
which is why you're the C.O.B., and I'm the captain.

175
00:06:17,960 --> 00:06:19,520
你是我的朋友  马库斯
You're my friend,  Marcus.

176
00:06:20,340 --> 00:06:22,710
但我再不会承认你是我的艇长
But you're no longer the captain of my boat.

177
00:06:22,880 --> 00:06:24,780
你还好意思穿着这身军装
That uniform you're still wearing?

178
00:06:24,940 --> 00:06:26,740
你根本不配
That's borrowed glory.

179
00:06:29,390 --> 00:06:31,390
我向来欣赏你的直言不讳  水手长
I've always appreciated your candor, C.O.B.

180
00:06:37,600 --> 00:06:38,740
锁上门  水手
Lock it up, sailor.

181
00:06:42,910 --> 00:06:44,020
你还好吗  上尉
You all right, lieutenant?

182
00:06:45,420 --> 00:06:46,380
