236
00:08:55,550 --> 00:08:57,220
从海底钓起来的
by a giant fish hook

237
00:08:57,220 --> 00:08:59,760
或是被愤怒的天神从天上扔下来的
or tossed down from the sky by angry gods.

238
00:08:59,760 --> 00:09:02,430
你若对岛民说大难将至  人人死无全尸
Telling an islander they're going to die violently

239
