Gentlemen.

244
00:09:30,730 --> 00:09:31,610
你也看到那架飞机了吧
You saw that plane?

245
00:09:31,610 --> 00:09:32,560
没错
Yeah.

246
00:09:32,750 --> 00:09:34,390
依我看  你们会遭遇到
I'd say you got yourself a bad case

247
00:09:34,390 --> 00:09:36,430
