Thanks for your help.

264
00:10:06,560 --> 00:10:07,990
还真挺解酒
That is good.

265
00:10:13,330 --> 00:10:14,670
我们潜艇上的十三名水手
13 of our sailors are about

266
00:10:14,670 --> 00:10:16,750
将在毫不了解敌方情况的状态下应战...
to face off with something they don't understand--

267
00:10:16,750 --> 00:10:18,180
