我的艇员呢
What about my crew?

222
00:09:03,920 --> 00:09:06,050
联邦监狱服刑7年
Seven years each in a federal penitentiary.

223
00:09:06,050 --> 00:09:07,290
不得假释
No parole.

224
00:09:07,350 --> 00:09:10,350
我们愿意放弃死刑制裁
Now, we are willing to forego the death penalty

225
00:09:10,350 --> 00:09:11,860
因为考虑到 
in light of the circumstance

226
00:09:11,860 --> 00:09:15,290
查普林艇长之子杰弗里不幸阵亡
regarding the unfortunate death of captain Chaplin's son Jeffrey.

227
00:09:16,370 --> 00:09:18,300
你想要我死  想封住我的嘴
You want me dead, you want to silence me,

228
00:09:18,300 --> 00:09:19,500
想杀光我的船员
you want to kill my crew?

229
00:09:19,500 --> 00:09:21,550
你有过机会  王八蛋  你错过了
You had your shot, you son of a bitch! You missed!

230
00:09:21,550 --> 00:09:24,220
你看清楚了  我不是政客
Look closely. I am not a politician.

231
00:09:24,220 --> 00:09:25,860
你敢再提我儿的名字
If you say my son's name again,

232
00:09:25,860 --> 00:09:29,130
我发誓  我就把你的眼珠子打出来
I swear I will crush the jelly from your eyes.

233
00:09:29,130 --> 00:09:30,730
好了  冷静  冷静
Okay. Easy, easy, easy.

234
00:09:30,730 --> 00:09:31,750
冷静点
Easy!

235
00:09:34,240 --> 00:09:35,300
别激动
Easy.

236
00:09:36,350 --> 00:09:37,880
把枪放下  没事了
Get them down. We're okay.

237
00:09:41,360 --> 00:09:42,760
没事了  没事了
We're okay. We're okay.

238
00:09:43,920 --> 00:09:45,050
没事了
We're okay.

239
00:09:47,760 --> 00:09:49,170
他的情绪不对  山姆
He's not well, Sam.

240
00:09:49,170 --> 00:09:51,140
你还有很多值得珍惜的东西
You still have something to live for.

241
00:09:51,150 --> 00:09:54,210
别把希望都寄托在一无所有的人身上
Don't tie it all to a man with nothing to lose.

242
00:10:04,410 --> 00:10:06,410
你不是说应该"不动声色"吗
What the hell happened to "Show no emotion"?

243
00:10:06,410 --> 00:10:08,720
你打破了自己制定的规则  我想...
You're breaking your own rules, sir. I'd like--

244
00:10:08,720 --> 00:10:09,780
长官
Sir!

245
00:10:11,670 --> 00:10:13,060
他惹怒我了
He pissed me off.

246
00:10:13,570 --> 00:10:14,680
他惹怒你了
He pissed you off?

247
00:10:15,420 --> 00:10:16,820
可现在他是唯一一位
That is the one man right now

248
00:10:16,920 --> 00:10:18,720
有权力送我们回家的人
who has the power to send us all back home!

249
00:10:18,720 --> 00:10:20,510
是送我们进监狱
To send us to prison.

250
00:10:20,750 --> 00:10:21,850
这是在谈判
It's a negotiation!

251
00:10:22,090 --> 00:10:23,580
双方各退一步  达成妥协
We give a little, they give a little.

252
00:10:23,580 --> 00:10:25,340
-我知道怎么谈判  -真的吗
- I know how it works. - Really?

253
00:10:25,340 --> 00:10:27,470
因为你刚才的表现  实在是太...
'Cause the man I saw in there seemed completely--

254
00:10:27,960 --> 00:10:28,790
继续说  说出来
Go on. Say it.

255
00:10:31,110 --> 00:10:33,540
长官  服五年  六年徒刑  我都能接受
I could do five years, sir. I could do six.

256
00:10:33,540 --> 00:10:35,350
-闭嘴  -只要能让我们回家
- Stop it! - If it gets us back home,

257
00:10:35,460 --> 00:10:37,420
只要不再有人员伤亡  我就愿意服刑
and no more people die, I could do it!

258
00:10:37,420 --> 00:10:38,590
那就是你想要的结局吗
Is that how you want this to end?

259
00:10:38,590 --> 00:10:40,600
不是想要  是除此之外别无他法
It's not what I want, it's what I can get.

260
00:10:41,900 --> 00:10:42,830
谁曾经那样教过我
Who taught me that?

261
00:10:43,080 --> 00:10:44,910
我还教过你  荣誉高于一切
And what did I teach you about honor?

262
00:10:47,320 --> 00:10:49,860
你知道只要你开口  我定会至死忠随
You know I will follow you all the way down if you ask.

263
00:10:50,030 --> 00:10:52,410
可是长官  你别指望他们向你道歉
But the apology you want is not coming, sir.

264
00:10:53,010 --> 00:10:55,120
他们是代表美国政府来交涉的
That is the United States of America in there!

265
00:10:55,450 --> 00:10:57,370
而美国政府从不道歉
And they do not apologize!

266
00:11:10,050 --> 00:11:12,420
一定要时刻注意你的氧气剩余量
Pay close attention to your air reserves.

267
00:11:12,580 --> 00:11:13,790
注意好绳索
And watch the tether.

268
00:11:13,900 --> 00:11:15,480
那是我们唯一的纽带
It's our only communication.

269
00:11:15,720 --> 00:11:18,500
如果绳索被切断  一定要保持深度
If you lose the tether, maintain your depth.

270
00:11:18,650 --> 00:11:20,480
因为如果任凭水流带你上浮得过快...
If the current drags you up too quickly--

271
00:11:20,480 --> 00:11:22,160
我就会被压扁  关节会炸开
I get bent. My joints explode.

272
00:11:22,160 --> 00:11:23,600
脑子里全是血栓  我见过那种惨状
My brain embolizes. I've seen it.

273
00:11:24,330 --> 00:11:26,040
我又不是第一次参加牛仔竞技了
This isn't my first rodeo, okay?

274
00:11:26,260 --> 00:11:28,060
孩子  她恐怕不知道牛仔竞技为何物吧
She don't know what a rodeo is, kid.

275
00:11:28,190 --> 00:11:30,980
-法国也会举办牛仔竞技啊  -不可能
