276
00:11:31,340 --> 00:11:34,550
真的  牛马满场奔腾  牛仔精彩献艺
Oui. Horses, cows, cowboys.

277
00:11:35,080 --> 00:11:37,630
法国根本没有牛仔  女士
There's no such thing as a French cowboy, lady.

278
00:11:37,780 --> 00:11:39,390
法国人就是牛仔的反义词
French is the opposite of cowboy.

279
00:11:39,390 --> 00:11:40,930
牛仔是像威尔・罗杰斯
Cowboy is like Will Rogers,

280
00:11:40,930 --> 00:11:43,370
约翰・韦恩和克林特・伊斯特伍德那样的真汉子
John Wayne, Clint Eastwood.

281
00:11:39,390 --> 00:11:43,370
三人均为美国演员  以饰演牛仔而闻名

282
00:11:43,370 --> 00:11:44,290
罗伯特・杜瓦尔也算吧
Robert Duvall?

283
00:11:43,370 --> 00:11:44,290
美国演员  以饰演牛仔而闻名

284
00:11:44,470 --> 00:11:45,380
你终于明白我的意思了
Now you're getting it.

285
00:11:45,500 --> 00:11:46,500
杜瓦尔是法国人
Duvall is French.

286
00:11:47,010 --> 00:11:48,510
收回你刚才的话
You take that back.

287
00:11:48,860 --> 00:11:50,240
我们要到达声呐阵列处了
We're coming up on the array now.

288
00:11:50,240 --> 00:11:51,840
每个人都要保持警觉  坚守岗...
I want everyone sharp, at their stat--

289
00:11:52,220 --> 00:11:53,690
你不是要用这把电钻吧
Tell me that's not the drill you're using.

290
00:11:53,950 --> 00:11:54,620
是啊
Yes.

291
00:11:54,850 --> 00:11:56,230
那可是把手提钻
It looks like a jackhammer.

292
00:11:56,440 --> 00:11:58,660
电池外壳上的螺栓足有10英寸长
The bolts in the battery casing are 10 inches long.

293
00:11:58,660 --> 00:11:59,760
不行  给他找把扳手来  水手长
No. Get him a wrench, C.O.B.

294
00:11:59,890 --> 00:12:01,440
要是用扳手  没等我拧下第一枚螺钉
A wrench? I'll suck down my first tank

295
00:12:01,440 --> 00:12:02,680
我的第一瓶氧气就该耗光了
before I pull the first screw.

296
00:12:02,790 --> 00:12:04,990
你只要在海里启动电钻  10英里内的潜艇
You rev that thing out there, and any sub within 10 miles

297
00:12:04,990 --> 00:12:07,630
就会向我艇发射MK48鱼雷
is gonna put a Mark-48 torpedo in our ear hole,

298
00:12:07,630 --> 00:12:08,750
造成艇毁人亡的后果
and we'll all be dead.

299
00:12:09,110 --> 00:12:10,140
为什么没有事先请示我
Why wasn't I told about this?

300
00:12:10,140 --> 00:12:13,410
查验执行任务所需的装备是艇长的工作
It's the job of the captain to review all the mission assets.

301
00:12:13,410 --> 00:12:14,890
我在半小时前刚接任了代理艇长一职
I was assigned this mission half an hour ago.

302
00:12:17,810 --> 00:12:19,810
好吧  就用电钻  但动作要快
Fine. Use the drill, but make it quick.

303
00:12:20,790 --> 00:12:21,320
什么
What?

304
00:12:21,600 --> 00:12:23,430
你得好好考虑清楚  上尉
You need to think this through, Lieutenant.

305
00:12:23,500 --> 00:12:25,210
你这么刚愎自用
You let your ego drive the boat,

306
00:12:25,210 --> 00:12:26,770
会把我们害死的
people will get dead.

307
00:12:33,440 --> 00:12:34,830
你之前答应过我格蕾丝不会
You said Grace wouldn't be charged

308
00:12:34,830 --> 00:12:36,220
与马库斯和山姆一起遭到起诉
along with Marcus and Sam.

309
00:12:36,220 --> 00:12:38,410
我们会为你女儿减刑
And we'll reduce the charges against your daughter

310
00:12:38,410 --> 00:12:41,240
前提是你说服艇长接受我们的条件
when you convince the captain to accept our terms.

311
00:12:41,240 --> 00:12:43,110
我与马库斯相识已有30年之久了
I've known Marcus for 30 years.

312
00:12:43,230 --> 00:12:44,790
他是个坚持原则的人
He will stand on principle.

313
00:12:45,270 --> 00:12:47,320
无论我说什么  都无法改变那一点
Nothing I can say is going to change that.

314
00:12:47,320 --> 00:12:49,870
伊利诺斯号的巴特勒艇长向我报告说
I have a message from Captain Butler of the "Illinois".

315
00:12:50,000 --> 00:12:52,620
他发现对方的的声纳阵列有个缺口
He believes he's found a gap in their sonar array line.

316
00:12:52,620 --> 00:12:55,220
他还需多久就能定位并击沉科罗拉多号呢
How long before he finds the "Colorado" and sinks her?

317
00:12:55,330 --> 00:12:57,190
那艘潜艇上可都是美国的水手
Those are American sailors on that submarine.

318
00:12:57,560 --> 00:12:58,820
有人则认为他们是一群罪犯
Some say they're criminals.

319
00:12:58,820 --> 00:13:00,730
虽然我并不愿意下达发射命令
Now I won't enjoy giving the fire order,

320
00:13:00,730 --> 00:13:02,590
但若到了紧要关头  我不得不发
but when the time comes, I will give it,

321
00:13:02,590 --> 00:13:03,680
换成你  也会这样做
just as you would.

322
00:13:04,420 --> 00:13:06,270
好好劝劝你的朋友  让他妥协吧
So convince your friend to settle.

323
00:13:13,900 --> 00:13:14,880
我到达声纳阵列了
All right, I'm on the array.

324
00:13:16,550 --> 00:13:18,180
很好  系好绳索
Good. Secure the tether.

325
00:13:18,400 --> 00:13:19,800
我要开始计时了
I'm starting the clock.

326
00:13:20,000 --> 00:13:21,590
预计空气余量

327
00:13:19,800 --> 00:13:21,660
能见度100英尺  看不到艇体
Vis 100 feet. Can't see the boat.

328
00:13:22,090 --> 00:13:23,400
我们就在你的正下方  詹姆斯
We're right below you, James.

329
00:13:23,530 --> 00:13:24,610
开始修理吧
Proceed with repair.

330
00:13:24,760 --> 00:13:26,800
先取出电池外壳上的螺栓
First remove the bolts from the battery casing.

331
00:13:31,650 --> 00:13:32,880
该死  谁听见了
Damn it. Who heard that?

332
00:13:32,880 --> 00:13:33,670
谁都能听见  长官
Who didn't, ma'am?

333
00:13:33,670 --> 00:13:34,600
噪音已传遍
We have noise propagation

334
00:13:34,600 --> 00:13:36,650
温跃层上下15英里的区域
above and below the thermal for 15 miles.

335
00:13:36,650 --> 00:13:39,000
全体注意  好戏开场了  我们成了活靶子
All right, people, it's a party, and we just became the pinata.

336
00:13:39,000 --> 00:13:41,570
金士官  请用你最快的速度完成
Petty Officer King, as fast as you can, please.

337
00:13:41,770 --> 00:13:43,630
-是  长官  -你是想害死我们吗
- Aye, ma'ma. - Are you trying to get us killed?

338
00:13:52,700 --> 00:13:53,740
难以置信
Unbelievable.

339
00:13:54,760 --> 00:13:56,080
肯德尔先生说你们有条件要提
Mr. Kendal says you have an offer?

340
