你误会了
You misunderstand.

343
00:14:03,880 --> 00:14:06,190
我要求在民事法庭公开审理
I demand a public trial in a civilian court

344
00:14:06,190 --> 00:14:07,330
全程录像  陪审员列席
cameras, jury,

345
00:14:07,470 --> 00:14:09,050
并且赦免我手下的全体艇员
amnesty for my enlisted men.

346
00:14:09,050 --> 00:14:11,290
我看你真的是疯了
You really have lost your mind.

347
00:14:11,920 --> 00:14:13,650
你还说他是认真的  肯德尔
Y-you said he was serious, Kendal.

348
00:14:13,650 --> 00:14:15,260
除非你们先答应这些条件
And only after you've agreed to those terms

349
00:14:15,260 --> 00:14:16,150
我们才愿意商谈在巴基斯坦海岸
will we discuss the six

350
00:14:16,150 --> 00:14:18,280
搭载那六名海豹突击队员的事
navy S.E.A.L.S I picked up off the coast of Pakistan.

351
00:14:25,420 --> 00:14:26,960
一定是这海边空气的原因
Must be all this ocean air.

352
00:14:27,350 --> 00:14:28,290
让我感觉非常饿
I'm famished.

353
00:14:28,670 --> 00:14:29,750
我们先暂停去吃个午饭吧
Shall we break for lunch?

354
00:14:31,680 --> 00:14:33,430
疯子以为这是场游戏
Lunatic thinks this is a game.

355
00:14:35,640 --> 00:14:37,200
伊利诺斯号已经穿越了边界
The "Illinois" is through the perimeter.

356
00:14:37,200 --> 00:14:39,410
两艘688i潜艇归航
Two 688i's inbound.

357
00:14:39,410 --> 00:14:41,090
追捕到它
Hunt her down.

358
00:14:41,440 --> 00:14:43,820
你一找到那艘潜艇  就立刻通知我
I want to know the moment you find that sub.

359
00:14:53,470 --> 00:14:54,930
詹姆斯  检查一下水压
James, check your pressure.

360
00:14:55,200 --> 00:14:56,520
收到  再拆一个螺栓
Copy that. One more bolt.

361
00:14:56,640 --> 00:14:57,700
詹姆斯  你得加快速度了
James, you need to hurry.

362
00:14:57,820 --> 00:14:58,500
或许他们没听到
Maybe they didn't hear it.

363
00:14:58,500 --> 00:14:59,780
或许他们在另一片区域
Maybe they're in another sector

364
00:14:59,780 --> 00:15:00,310
没有...
and they didn't--

365
00:15:00,500 --> 00:15:02,520
发现新目标  2艘688潜艇  
New contact--2 688-class subs

366
00:15:02,530 --> 00:15:03,540
方位0-7-1度
bearing 0-7-1,

367
00:15:03,540 --> 00:15:05,000
距离16000码
range 16,000 yards.

368
