16000码  还很远
16k? They're too far away.

369
00:15:06,980 --> 00:15:07,460
运气好一点
With a little luck,

370
00:15:07,460 --> 00:15:08,910
我们很快就可以撤退...
we'll be outhere before they fi--

371
00:15:08,910 --> 00:15:10,350
