New contact-- Virginia Class.

372
00:15:10,350 --> 00:15:11,500
我们的挡音区声纳有反应  长官
Much have come out of our baffles, ma'am.

373
00:15:11,680 --> 00:15:12,710
是伊利诺斯号  已经很近了
It's the "Illinois." She's close.

374
00:15:14,570 --> 00:15:15,930
你必须命令下潜了  上尉
You gotta dive the boat, lieutenant.

375
00:15:16,140 --> 00:15:17,580
不  他还在外面呢
No! He's still outside!

376
00:15:17,580 --> 00:15:19,340
探测到主动声纳  它在搜寻我们
Active sonar. She's looking for us.

377
00:15:19,340 --> 00:15:20,350
立刻下潜
Dive the boat now.

378
00:15:20,350 --> 00:15:21,920
安静  我知道自己在干什么
Quiet! I know what I'm doing.

379
00:15:21,920 --> 00:15:23,330
如果我们下潜  他必死无疑
He's dead if we dive!

380
00:15:23,460 --> 00:15:25,300
目标正在靠近  航向1-4-9度
Contact coming about. Heading 1-4-9.

381
00:15:26,470 --> 00:15:27,550
格蕾丝
Grace.

382
00:15:30,320 --> 00:15:32,740
舵手  左满舵  紧急下潜
Helm, left full rudder! Emergency deep!

383
00:15:32,940 --> 00:15:34,240
下潜吧  凯希尔先生
Take us down, Mr. Cahill.

384
00:15:34,810 --> 00:15:36,980
詹姆斯  切断绳索  詹姆斯
James, cut the tether. James?

385
00:15:37,480 --> 00:15:39,090
收到请回复  切断绳索
Do you copy? Cut the tether.

386
00:15:39,350 --> 00:15:41,790
什么  不  没有绳索我就完了
What? No. I'm screwed without the tether.

387
00:15:42,950 --> 00:15:44,000
别那么做
Don't do it!

388
00:15:45,620 --> 00:15:46,260
不要
No!

389
00:16:06,280 --> 00:16:07,530
超过测试深度
Passing test depth.

390
00:16:08,710 --> 00:16:10,260
等等  他切断绳子了吗
Wait. Did he cut loose?

391
00:16:10,390 --> 00:16:11,760
我们目前在1400英尺海下  索菲
We're at 1,400 feet, Sophie.

392
00:16:11,760 --> 00:16:13,640
如果他还连着  就必死无疑  安静点
If he's attached, he's dead. Now be quiet.

